HEADWORD: Irreconcilable
<hw>Ir*rec"on*ci`la*ble</hw> <pr>(?; 277)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[Pref. <ets>ir-</ets> not + <ets>reconcilable</ets>: cf. F.
<ets>irr⟦eacute⟧conciliable</ets>.]</ety> <def>Not reconcilable; not
able to be reconciled or brought into accord; implacable; incompatible;
inconsistent; disagreeing; <as>as, <ex>irreconcilable</ex> enemies,
statements</as>.</def> -- <wordforms><wf>Ir*rec"on*ci`la*ble*ness</wf>,
<pos>n.</pos> -- <wf>Ir*rec"on*ci`la*bly</wf>,
<pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
